    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 170, Number 62 (Thursday, April 11, 2024)][House]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href="https://www.gpo.gov">www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. FOSTER:H.R. 7948.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:This bill is enacted pursuant to the power granted toCongress under Article I, Section 8, Clauses 1 and 18 of theUnited States Constitution.The single subject of this legislation is:Adds an allowance for broadband internet to the utilityallowance provided to families with children in HUD housingprograms.[Page H2317]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
